## Processing Templates

### Atomic Scale Processing
```python
@77d_template(scale="atomic", device="microscope")
def atomic_structure_analysis(molecular_data):
    # Molecular-level processing
    expanded = expand_dimensions(molecular_data, dimensions=77)
    analyzed = quantum_analyze(expanded)
    compressed = fractal_compress(analyzed, ratio=100)
    return atomic_optimized(compressed)
```

### Urban Scale Processing
```python
@77d_template(scale="urban", device="satellite")
def city_planning_optimization(urban_data):
    # City-wide multi-dimensional processing
    expanded = expand_dimensions(urban_data, dimensions=77)
    simulated = population_simulate(expanded)
    optimized = ecological_optimize(simulated)
    compressed = fractal_compress(optimized, ratio=1000)
    return urban_optimized(compressed)
```

### Universal Scale Processing
```python
@77d_template(scale="universal", device="supercomputer")
def cosmic_structure_modeling(galactic_data):
    # Universal scale processing
    expanded = expand_dimensions(galactic_data, dimensions=77)
    evolved = cosmic_evolution_simulate(expanded)
    rendered = photonic_render(evolved)
    compressed = quantum_compress(rendered, ratio=10)
    return universal_optimized(compressed)
```

