## Usage Examples

### Multi-Scale Processing
```python
from d77_dataset import load_multi_scale_dataset

# Load appropriate dataset for device
dataset = load_multi_scale_dataset(device_type="auto_detect")

# Process entity across multiple scales
result = dataset.process_multi_scale(
    entity_data=input_data,
    scales=["atomic", "object", "building", "city"],
    quality="ultra_realistic"
)
```

### Device-Specific Processing
```python
# Optimize for specific device
mobile_result = dataset.process_for_device(entity_data, "smartphone")
satellite_result = dataset.process_for_device(entity_data, "satellite")
microscope_result = dataset.process_for_device(entity_data, "microscope")
```

### Training Custom Models
```python
# Fine-tune for specific application
custom_model = dataset.train_custom_model(
    training_data=dataset.dimensional_data,
    target_scale="planetary",
    optimization_goal="realism"
)
```

